data.title: Episode 2550 (11 July 2003)
data.meta_description: Anthony bids farewell to the Square, Alfie is devastated by Kat, and Dennis puts himself on the line to help a friend. Doctor Anthony Trueman - Nicholas R. Bailey Patrick Trueman - Rudolph Walker Alfie Moon - Shane Richie Kat Slater - Jessie Wallace 'Nana' Victoria Moon - Hilda Braid Paul...
data.text:
Kat cries in bed.

Patrick tells Anthony about his grandfather.

Alfie tells Nana Moon about his date with Kat.

Dennis is worried when a friend arrives.

Alfie gets a call from Kat and tells him she's resigning.

Dennis tells Tony he's going to see the boss.

Paul agrees to meet Anthony for a drink and manages to reconcile Anthony and Patrick.

Alfie tries to write to Kat.

Dan thinks that Kate is good looking.

Kat tells Anthony about Alfie.

Nana Moon tells Alfie to tell Kat that he loves her.

Dennis asks Dalton for Â£20,000 for keeping quiet.

Phil gives Laura money for the baby.

Sonia tells Patrick that Anthony has inspired her. Anthony says goodbye to Paul.

Kat just wants to be friends with Alfie.

Patrick tells Anthony to go and seek his fortune and to have fun.
